        {
            "title": "美國國債全線上漲 鮑威爾發言促使交易員上調聯儲會9月降息押注",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"633\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ytwAmq5O5L3N1PwZkdCFyw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/e146d7310498c30831e38d0c5df2bfb7\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 美國國債上漲，此前聯儲會主席傑羅姆·<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:鮑威爾;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/鮑威爾\">鮑威爾</a>謹慎地為9月降息打開了大門，指出儘管通膨擔憂依然存在，但勞動力市場的風險上升。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">各期限國債殖利率均下跌，兩年期國債殖利率一度下跌7個基點，而基準10年期國債殖利率則跌至4.27%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「在我們考慮政策立場的變化之際，失業率和其他勞動力市場指標的穩定使我們能夠謹慎行事，」鮑威爾在為周五懷俄明州傑克遜霍爾年度會議所準備的講話稿中指出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀聯儲會主席鮑威爾：風險平衡的變化或使調整政策立場成為恰當之舉</p><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\" \" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"633\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/gpVyj8Vb4ANWsDP8Q4FYLg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYzMztjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/311bd38bc1bf3891adfadd428449259e\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\"> </figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易員立即上調對聯儲會9月降息25個基點的押注。利率互換顯示降息的可能性超過85%，而在鮑威爾開始講話之前，這一可能性僅為65%左右。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「鮑威爾的講話聽起來略顯鴿派，暗示風險從美國通膨的粘性轉向勞動力市場的走弱，」法國農業信貸銀行G-10外匯研究與策略主管Valentin Marinov表示，「他的言論似乎進一步為9月降息鋪平了道路。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Treasuries Jump as Powell Says Risks May Warrant Adjusting Rates</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%82%B5%E5%85%A8%E7%B7%9A%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2-%E9%AE%91%E5%A8%81%E7%88%BE%E7%99%BC%E8%A8%80%E4%BF%83%E4%BD%BF%E4%BA%A4%E6%98%93%E5%93%A1%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E8%81%AF%E5%84%B2%E6%9C%839%E6%9C%88%E9%99%8D%E6%81%AF%E6%8A%BC%E6%B3%A8-143137569.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-08-22 23:00:39",
